{"tid":1246832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"禍延財會 公務員加薪等撥款恐受拖累","createTime":"2019-06-21T01:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:34:43.000Z","uid":56881,"like":634,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"89630c362f9dea62dd462bb43ce83ef278a0c728","tid":1246832,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A6%8D%E5%BB%B6%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E7%AD%89%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%90%E5%8F%97%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-214500706.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A6%258D%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B4%25AF-214500706.html&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a7827e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A6%8D%E5%BB%B6%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E7%AD%89%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%90%E5%8F%97%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-214500706.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1MQrxXN.mpnNf5oZkSFjeQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/97be2f5677eefe5fb73e97d8b0fa1fba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1MQrxXN.mpnNf5oZkSFjeQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F97be2f5677eefe5fb73e97d8b0fa1fba&h=29fcfc05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》亂局影響立法會財委會審議撥款的進度。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】修訂《逃犯條例》亂局禍延立法會財務委員會（財委會）運作及審議撥款進度，據悉，目前政府及建制派仍在觀望今日財委會能否正常審議，若民主派就反修例「拉布」或阻撓會議進行，在此惡劣環境下，憂慮隨時影響公務員加薪等多項撥款未能在暑假休會前通過。<br />\n<br />\n休會前或僅通過一兩項<br />\n<br />\n據了解，現時政府及建制派視今日的財委會運作為重要指標，若能正常審議，以目前十多個小時會議時間，隨時能通過十多項至二十項撥款，但若幾近完全未能審議，則要考慮往後加會是否仍有作用，而且休會前隨時僅能通過一兩項撥款。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前財委會議程上有二十一項議程，但據知有多項重要撥款仍未包括在內，例如公務員薪酬調整及理順公營小學校長及副校長的薪酬，若前者未能在暑假休會前通過，意味公務員要延遲加薪數個月，其時勢必引起公務員反彈；若後者未能在休會前通過，就會影響新學年未能即時實施校長薪酬調整。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往做法，立法會多數會在公務員加薪撥款中讓步，盡量在暑假休會前通過，但現時立法會情況特殊及太多變數，若環境惡劣至幾近完全無法審議，政府及立法會會否確保公務員加薪方案在暑假休會前通過，仍屬未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公務員先唔洗驚<br />\n拖都有得date back返"},{"pid":"ad7fe00d63438242600a013893b8427efabba72e","tid":1246832,"uid":16061,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"有撚所謂 有拖無欠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877d7720539b1803ccf6a3ffabb09cc59c437a7","tid":1246832,"uid":134834,"like":349,"dislike":4,"score":345,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"呢個真 佢會back pay返<br />\n公務員驚咩"},{"pid":"be4c4c366700f9bd4133f3d42d9ceaec0242ce33","tid":1246832,"uid":83487,"like":230,"dislike":2,"score":228,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"仲好 呢排太大洗 可以幫我儲下錢<br />\n<br />\n利申 公務撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dafec0429aaafb05448cc9dfbb3cb1aeecafd0","tid":1246832,"uid":51701,"like":163,"dislike":2,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:28.000Z","msg":"公務員表示支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eb95d0e487e8504193bb000900beccf546ae4f","tid":1246832,"uid":41411,"like":66,"dislike":12,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"其時勢必引起公務員反彈<br />\n<br />\nWFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa130263b4bea330bca1ce110dbf1ba291c644ea","tid":1246832,"uid":61520,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簽名數字不要低得難看啊！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-