"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"分化番佢囉~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果唔係林鄭搞到咁殭<br />\n而家早就加咗人工啦!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e95fa5d363e885d6a6f1658e67344ac3436053d0","tid":1246832,"uid":47190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"無所謂，反正遲啲會通過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d975fda5d89a3ba44f6d63a1058aecde061185c","tid":1246832,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89630c362f9dea62dd462bb43ce83ef278a0c728","tid":1246832,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A6%8D%E5%BB%B6%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E7%AD%89%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%90%E5%8F%97%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-214500706.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A6%258D%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B4%25AF-214500706.html&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=a7827e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A6%8D%E5%BB%B6%E8%B2%A1%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA%E7%AD%89%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%81%90%E5%8F%97%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF-214500706.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1MQrxXN.mpnNf5oZkSFjeQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/97be2f5677eefe5fb73e97d8b0fa1fba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1MQrxXN.mpnNf5oZkSFjeQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F97be2f5677eefe5fb73e97d8b0fa1fba&h=29fcfc05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》亂局影響立法會財委會審議撥款的進度。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】修訂《逃犯條例》亂局禍延立法會財務委員會（財委會）運作及審議撥款進度，據悉，目前政府及建制派仍在觀望今日財委會能否正常審議，若民主派就反修例「拉布」或阻撓會議進行，在此惡劣環境下，憂慮隨時影響公務員加薪等多項撥款未能在暑假休會前通過。<br />\n<br />\n休會前或僅通過一兩項<br />\n<br />\n據了解，現時政府及建制派視今日的財委會運作為重要指標，若能正常審議，以目前十多個小時會議時間，隨時能通過十多項至二十項撥款，但若幾近完全未能審議，則要考慮往後加會是否仍有作用，而且休會前隨時僅能通過一兩項撥款。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前財委會議程上有二十一項議程，但據知有多項重要撥款仍未包括在內，例如公務員薪酬調整及理順公營小學校長及副校長的薪酬，若前者未能在暑假休會前通過，意味公務員要延遲加薪數個月，其時勢必引起公務員反彈；若後者未能在休會前通過，就會影響新學年未能即時實施校長薪酬調整。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往做法，立法會多數會在公務員加薪撥款中讓步，盡量在暑假休會前通過，但現時立法會情況特殊及太多變數，若環境惡劣至幾近完全無法審議，政府及立法會會否確保公務員加薪方案在暑假休會前通過，仍屬未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公務員先唔洗驚<br />\n拖都有得date back返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"東方又想吹到公務員為咗加薪不成吊200萬人<br />\n<br />\n大家最緊要睇source同fact check"},{"pid":"c733d07e8e949983e43a59280b3260f50634ce23","tid":1246832,"uid":186961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"都估到實拎呢個做籌碼<br />\n等班無腦公務員嘈我哋阻q住哂<br />\n<br />\n我又唔等錢洗, 當儲錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97592fd7863456952f19631e5e8576c9efd73256","tid":1246832,"uid":255148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂 <br />\n遲咪遲<br />\n驚撚呀"},{"pid":"68fd8af34c2afcb4ec0d65ae4165794d6c0f0ee4","tid":1246832,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"對唔過三皮公務員仲要一次過出 交少d mpf"},{"pid":"553d30f2a8563bb2b737ef0e54af95b059376d8f","tid":1246832,"uid":70789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂，當儲下錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324657402f9beead16935ba8766380996ab4062c","tid":1246832,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"公務猿唔係有得追溯返？"},{"pid":"292368418299678594d52cf79f69ddc7ca2af0d2","tid":1246